{"lemma":"خُرْسُ","slug":"خُرْسُ","root":"خ.ر.س","root_slug":"خ-ر-س","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ر-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10323","","n10327","n10328","n10329"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B3%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to mute, to shut down"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"mute"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Color or defect adjective from the root خ ر س (ḵ r s)."},"ipa":["/ʔax.ra.sa/","/ʔax.ras/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10323","headword_ar":"خَرِسَ","root":"xrs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarasN","text_ar":"خَرَسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was dumb; was naturally, by conformation, prevented from speaking;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was destitute of the faculty of speech, by natural conformation, like the beast:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axorasu","text_ar":"اَخْرَسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, tonguetied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"withheld from speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"either from inability to find words to express what he would say,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by natural conformation"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the organs of speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarisa Almajolisu","text_ar":"خَرِسَ المَجْلِسُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The assembly was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, mute,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speechless."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarasa AlmaroA^apa","text_ar":"خَرَسَ المَرْاَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh, IAth,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh,) [inf. n., app.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarosN","text_ar":"خَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fed the woman with what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurosap","text_ar":"خُرْسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Lh, IAth;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fed her on the occasion of child-birth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xr~s","text_ar":"خرّس","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalyhaA","text_ar":"عَليهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxoriysN","text_ar":"تَخْرِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxorisapN","text_ar":"تَخْرِسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) In like manner you say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xr~shaA","text_ar":"خرّسهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxoriysN","text_ar":"تَخْرِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xrs EanohaA","text_ar":"خرس عَنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [so in the TA, without any syll. signs to the verb;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made for her what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurosap","text_ar":"خُرْسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurisato","text_ar":"خُرِسَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurisato","text_ar":"خُرِسَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in a copy of the A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She was fed with what is so termed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a feast on the occasion of her having given birth to a child was made for her."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarisa","text_ar":"خَرِسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drank from the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of wine-jar called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaros","text_ar":"خَرْس"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sgh, K,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dan~","text_ar":"دَنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","S","A","Lh","IAth","L","Sgh"]},{"entry_id":"n10327","headword_ar":"خَرْسٌ","root":"xrs","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wine-jar such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dan~","text_ar":"دَنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (JK, S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xirosN","text_ar":"خِرْسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kr, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiroSN","text_ar":"خِرْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoraAsN","text_ar":"اَخْرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuruwsN","text_ar":"خُرُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["Kr","K","TA","JK"]},{"entry_id":"n10328","headword_ar":"خُرْسٌ","root":"xrs","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Food that is prepared on the occasion of the birth of a child;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiraAsN","text_ar":"خِرَاسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lh, TA.) IJ seems to assign to it also the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurosapN","text_ar":"خُرْسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  Hence, as also ↓ the second word,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A feast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"banquet, that is prepared on that occasion, and to which people are invited:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in a trad. of Hassán,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna A_i*aA duEiYa A_ilaY","text_ar":"كَانَ اـِذَا دُعِىَ اـِلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEaAmK qaAla A_ilaY EurosK A^amo xurosK A^amo A_iEo*aArK","text_ar":"طَعَامٍ قَالَ اـِلَى عُرْسٍ اَمْ خُرْسٍ اَمْ اـِعْذَارٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He used, when he was invited to food, to say, To a weddingfeast, or a feast for child-birth, or a circumcisionfeast?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and if it were for one of these, he consented: but if not, he did not consent. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10329","headword_ar":"خِرْسٌ","root":"xrs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarosN","text_ar":"خَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}